Section 16: Removing Spring Boot
    Lecture 85: Spring AOP Configuration

1. Remove Spring boot aop auto configuration
 1.1 Add Spring aop property to change
    - src/main/resources/application.properties file
    - add "spring.autoconfigure.exclude[7]=org.springframework.boot.autoconfigure.aop.AopAutoConfiguration"
      property in the application.properties file

2. setup core Spring AOP configuration
  2.1 Create new AOP Configuration ej.springframework.config.AopConfig.java
  2.2 Add @Configuration annotation on the AopConfig class
  2.2 Add @EnableAspectJAutoProxy annotation on the AopConfig class to activate the Core Spring AOP

3. Test
  3.1 Start Server
  3.2 Open localhost:8080
  3.3 Check Displayed data (i.e, Product list and Product items ...)
  3.4 login using wrong id and check weather still working application
  3.5 Check the console messages